verbose_text: Positive VEGF expression in the portal structures in liver tissues in both BDs and AWs had 0.847, 0.820 area under ROC, 80.0%, 77.1% sensitivity, 89.5%, 86.8% specificity, 87.5%, 84.4% PPV, 82.5%, 80.5% NPV and 84.9%, 82.19% accuracy respectively for BDs and AWs in discriminating between BA and non BA (p < 0.0001).
